A flashback of the weekend.

Our Global Entrepreurship students, from the High School Summer Abroad Program visited the beautiful city of Potsdam, located just outside Berlin, where they toured part of the city, its impressive gardens and the Sanssouci Palace, which was the summer residence of Frederick the Great, former king of Prussia. ❤️🇩🇪

There are only a few days left in the program, but we know they are still enjoying every excursion to the fullest! 
❤️🇩🇪💫

